                <div style="float: left;">
                        <p>
Best practices are generally and informally recognized as the methods and processes that have been shown over time to be superior to those achieved by other means.                         </p>
                                            <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">
                            <a title="tag wiki" href="/tags/best-practices/info">learn more&hellip;</a>
